            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;(get attributes bug 3) &lt;code&gt;/(\w+)=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/&lt;/code&gt; Optional whitespace should be allowed around the equal sign.&lt;/span&gt;

