            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;(html split bug 1) &lt;code&gt;s/&amp;gt;/&amp;gt;\n/g&lt;/code&gt; Since &quot;&amp;gt;&quot; is allowed in data, this may split text lines and confuse subsequent processing.&lt;/span&gt;

