            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I sometimes escape unnecessarily when I&apos;m unsure if something is special character or not. I&apos;ve edited the answer; it works the same but more concise.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/217867/lonnie-best&quot; title=&quot;8,494 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Lonnie Best&lt;/a&gt;
