                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment62568124_10844758&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2016-05-31 07:23:11Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;May 31, 2016 at 7:23&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This does not work. For the input &apos;&amp;lt;x a=&quot;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;y&amp;gt;&apos; the matches are x and y, although x is terminated.&lt;/span&gt;

