&lt;p&gt;I need to match all of these opening tags:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-html s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-name&quot;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-name&quot;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-attr&quot;&gt;href&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But not these:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-html s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-name&quot;&gt;br&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-name&quot;&gt;hr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-attr&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I came up with this and wanted to make sure I&apos;ve got it right. I am only capturing the &lt;code&gt;a-z&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-html s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-xml&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;([a-z]+) *[^/]*?&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I believe it says:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find a less-than, then&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find (and capture) a-z one or more times, then&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find zero or more spaces, then&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find any character zero or more times, greedy, except &lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;, then&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find a greater-than&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do I have that right? And more importantly, what do you think?&lt;/p&gt;
